OL,5, More than 16,000 people have signed an 
OL,6, open letter calling on the BBC to      
OL,7, apologise for an online news article   
OL,8, about trans women and lesbians.        
OL,10,FThe piece, published on Tuesday, quoted
OL,11,Flesbians who felt "pressured into sex  
OL,12,Fby some trans women".                  
OL,14,FThe letter described the article as    
OL,15,F"incredibly dangerous" and said it had 
OL,16,Fused a "deeply flawed study".          
OL,18,FThe BBC said it must "ensure debate and
OL,19,Fmake sure a wide a range of voices are 
OL,20,Fheard".                                
